      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43500.0,
